title: VA Sinners Lounge - Latin Sessions (2 of 2 CD) (2006) [ChillOut]
description:
VA Sinners Lounge - Latin Sessions (2 of 2 CD)
Year Of Release: 2006
Bitrate: 192-320 kbps

I purchased this cd along with along with Sinners Lounge: The Erotic Sessions, and I honestly prefer this cd over the other. Not to say that the "Erotic Sessions" is inferior in any way, but I just happened to favor this compilation. If you dont have Sinners Lounge: The Erotic Sessions it is a great companion to this compilation along with the host of Erotic Lounge compilations. The only flaw this collection of songs has is the inconsistency within the songs. You go from listening to blissfull guitars and seductive beats to dancefloor bass, and that should be a sin. With the exception of a few tracks, this is an excellent soundtrack, but it is even more enjoyable when in the company of someone else, be it early in the morning or late in the afternoon.
